                        text="&lt;p>I’m an avid sci-fi reader. I have read the Lord of Rings books more times than I can count and over time, have enjoyed discovering new authors. I spend lots of time with my family and enjoy long bike rides and seeing what is out there. I’ll bring my phone on these rides but only to take photos.&lt;/p>&lt;p>There is a lot of life going on. I’m not going to miss it.&lt;/p>"/>
